{"tid":1853534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(TVB又輸) 王晶《肥龍過江》香港票房仆街, 大陸取消上映","createTime":"2020-01-31T04:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:15:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":338,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"98892bf6e5e10217f875834b9dc3441b76b53cb8","tid":1853534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"《肥龍過江》- CCTVB出品, 王晶編劇/監製/主演<br />\n<br />\n結果《肥龍過江》榮登香港賀歲片票房包尾, 票房連葉念琛電影《我的筍盤男友》都不如 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/73257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F73257&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=57c783d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/73257</a><br />\n<br />\n而家,《肥龍過江》係大陸取消上映, 直接流放到網絡首播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/2159863893/Is0udmVLx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2F2159863893%2FIs0udmVLx&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=aca7cbbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/2159863893/Is0udmVLx</a><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://na.cx/i/F5sgoP2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5sgoP2.jpg&h=c7c6f892&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d4bb4ff457b0ba59778a83d1b352f37486c7d1c","tid":1853534,"uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":35,"score":-20,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:43:49.000Z","msg":"可惜黃百鳴《家有囍事2020》票房依然理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過黃百鳴同王晶始終有Ｄ分別。自反送中抗爭開始後，黃百鳴好似無咩公開支持止暴制亂。 反而王晶不斷公開支持止暴制亂兼屌義士，而且屌埋連登。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/5zz1FcE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zz1FcE.jpg&h=c4f64be0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ce260b1e4eb95080f344be66bac7f2301de25f3","tid":1853534,"uid":134071,"like"